  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述教育课堂服务（Education ClassroomService）的安全握手流程。整个流程从Start开始，先发送ClientHello，然后等待ServerHello。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Start",
        "SendClientHello",
        "WaitServerHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Start作为入口状态，然后到SendClientHello，再到WaitServerHello。那收到有效的ServerHello之后呢？下一步是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitServerHello",
        "SendClientHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "收到有效的ServerHello后，进入DeriveHPKE状态，完成密钥派生，然后发送认证信息到SendAuth状态，接着进入WaitAuth等待认证结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "SendAuth",
        "WaitAuth",
        "WaitServerHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了DeriveHPKE、SendAuth和WaitAuth这几个状态，以及它们之间的转移。WaitAuth之后应该有两个分支吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "SendAuth",
        "WaitAuth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，WaitAuth这里要分叉：认证成功就进入Established状态，认证失败则进入Error状态。分别标注为\"auth ok\"和\"auth fail\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitAuth",
        "Established",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Established和Error两个终态分支。那Established之后还有后续状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Established",
        "Error",
        "WaitAuth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，Established之后如果触发SessionKeyUpdate，就要进入Rekey状态进行密钥更新，更新完成后再回到Established。这是一个循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Established",
        "Rekey",
        "SessionKeyUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程从Education_ClassroomService进入Start，经过握手认证到达Established，之后可以循环进行Rekey密钥更新。我检查一下：SendClientHello、WaitServerHello、DeriveHPKE、SendAuth、WaitAuth、Established、Rekey、Error，所有状态和转移关系都已正确绘制。",
